data.description: Embrace the charm of this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom stucco home ideally located right in the heart of town. This property boasts a 2-car garage, a generous yard with mature trees, and an eat-in kitchen. While it needs some updating, it presents an excellent opportunity for customization and personalization.
